      children: "Turkey is on its way to becoming a supply chain hub for the European energy transition. Increased government attention to renewable energy policy has bolstered financial stability, attracted foreign investment, and allowed clean capacity to flourish. At the same time, Turkey balances its policy environment with enough local content requirements to incentivize domestic manufacturing."
